00:18:05.119 --> 00:18:21.119
When I was young, my father wrote to me the Bible verse, your word is a lamp to my foot and a light for my path. And he said, keep that always in mind. Remember God's word and live by it.

00:18:21.119 --> 00:18:38.309
I was born in 1929 in the city of Furu, Estonia. My family was religious and my God-fearing parents lovingly cared for me and provided everything that a child would need.

00:18:38.309 --> 00:18:54.339
When my father learned the truth, he gave each of us a Bible and we began to study it together. My father was arrested in the summer of 1948.

00:18:55.339 --> 00:19:05.339
Estonia was now under the Soviet regime, but he was still working as a school teacher. The local Department of Education asked him to come by.

00:19:05.339 --> 00:19:19.089
He went dressed in summer clothes and wearing sandals, and he never came back.

00:19:19.089 --> 00:19:30.430
At midnight, we heard someone banging at the door. We opened it and soldiers came in and demanded our passports.

00:19:30.430 --> 00:19:36.430
We put the passports on the table and they just said, you are under arrest.

00:19:36.430 --> 00:19:48.430
Pugged a prison in Tallinn was a place everyone was afraid of, and I was afraid too.

00:19:48.430 --> 00:19:57.430
I remember that I was taken down the steps to the basement, to a long corridor. There was nothing in the cell besides a bench.

00:20:01.950 --> 00:20:06.950
They slammed the door shut and that is when I became a little scared.

00:20:06.950 --> 00:20:22.460
But then I prayed to Jehovah to help me and a sense of peace came over me. I lay down on the bench and fell asleep.

00:20:22.460 --> 00:20:28.460
I was given a 10-year prison sentence as an enemy of the state.

00:20:28.460 --> 00:20:38.039
A year later, we were transferred to Russian prison camps.

00:20:38.039 --> 00:20:44.039
Spiritual food was hard to get. It couldn't be sent by mail.

00:20:44.039 --> 00:20:53.019
But the angels somehow still provided for us and we always had something.

00:20:53.019 --> 00:20:58.019
Even a single verse or a good thought can help in prison.

00:20:58.019 --> 00:21:08.019
In any case, God's word should be in our heart. We should never forget it, even if we can only remember one verse.

00:21:08.019 --> 00:21:18.430
